examples.en: The media are engaging in sensationalism.

examples.en: He declined engaging himself to secrecy.

examples.en: The lamp got broken when the kids were engaging in a little horseplay.

examples.en: The cast and crew were able to bring off an eccentric but engaging reinterpretation of King Lear.
